snippet.title: Shephy - Overview and gameplay
snippet.description:
Overview and Gameplay of the 1 player game, Shephy. Designed and Illustrated by Pawn and Published by Bouken. It was released on November 16, 2013 at the Tokyo Games Market.

If you have questions about anything in the video, please let me know in the comments and I'll be glad to answer them. You can also catch me on twitter!

Twitter: https://twitter.com/zenxacred

If you liked it, do hit the Like button. If you want more, don't forget to subscribe!

Also, would you kindly share this video? I would really appreciate it. :)

Thanks for watching!
